{"tid":929641,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我愛你 你愛她","createTime":"2018-12-05T17:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T15:34:15.000Z","uid":202425,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d6ceaa7aabd77a383a4614bc8e1b079a8f1d43","tid":929641,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T17:58:59.000Z","msg":"仲未放得低佢，但佢好似鍾意咗其他人了。<br />\n明明當時係你話一世，係你話唔會扔低我。<br />\n當時係你話你唔可以無咗我，係你話要陪我行教堂，係你話要娶我，係你話除咗我之外，你個個都唔要。<br />\n分咗手後，我留過你好多次，你覺得我只係唔捨得同唔甘心，當我冷靜返，我就會知我哋嘅問題係無得解決。<br />\n但點解，我到宜家仲會掛住你，因為你而喊醒，發夢見到你會笑。<br />\n好掛住你，我仲好愛你，可唔可以重新開始？<br />\n你係唯一一個令我相信愛情，同時令我唔敢再相信嘅人。<br />\n我愛你。"},{"pid":"dd702653ad0ec57d9d4000ae97f32fbddb0a0b0a","tid":929641,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T17:59:35.000Z","msg":"冇人愛你"},{"pid":"783dbe1d89f1d442ded6e4224f587325b441dadb","tid":929641,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd702653ad0ec57d9d4000ae97f32fbddb0a0b0a","tid":929641,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T17:59:35.000Z","msg":"冇人愛你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"真係無"},{"pid":"341965cc8126de7abd4946cc40d997b2ff64e001","tid":929641,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:08:49.000Z","msg":"時間沖淡啦唉"},{"pid":"1801492d81110999754f4e408350119cff025015","tid":929641,"uid":161122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:09:31.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d88d4ff28edd6002c5617b32809e29b23690a8","tid":929641,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:09:44.000Z","msg":"我愛你 你愛她 她愛茶<br />\n<br />\n伊藤園日式綠茶<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">廣告slogan</div>"},{"pid":"be0921c331cdcc1fa77d06c3af6f5f7aeca3ea6f","tid":929641,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8d88d4ff28edd6002c5617b32809e29b23690a8","tid